<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36" version="29.2.9"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="Zr49pj-jisf4JzkRYPB5"> <mxGraphModel dx="1106" dy="-535" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml
title GreenRoute: Professional Application Lifecycle State Diagram

' Main Application States
state \"App Launched\" as Launched
state \"Unauthenticated (Guest)\" as Guest {
 state \"Login Screen\" as Login
 state \"Registration\" as Reg
 [*] --> Login
 Login -right-> Reg : Sign Up
 Reg -left-> Login : Registration Success
}

state \"Authenticated Session\" as Auth {
 state \"Role Decision\" as Role <<choice>>
 
 state \"Driver Mode\" as Driver {
 state \"Dashboard \" as D_Idle
 state \"Trip Active\" as D_Active
 [*] --> D_Idle
 D_Idle --> D_Active : Start Trip (Fetch Route)
 D_Active --> D_Idle : Stop Trip
 }

 state \"Passenger Mode\" as Passenger {
 state \"Search View\" as P_Search
 state \"Live Map\" as P_Map
 state \"Notification Received\" as P_Notif
 
 [*] --> P_Search
 P_Search --> P_Map : Select Route
 P_Map --> P_Map : Apply Smoothing Algorithm
 P_Map --> P_Notif : [Proximity < 500m]
 P_Notif --> P_Map : Dismiss
 P_Map --> P_Search : Close Map
 }

 state \"Admin Mode\" as Admin {
 state \"Fleet Dashboard\" as A_Dash
 state \"Data Entry\" as A_Entry
 [*] --> A_Dash
 A_Dash --> A_Entry : Manage Bus/Route
 A_Entry --> A_Dash : Save Changes
 }

 [*] --> Role
 Role --> Driver : [Role: Driver]
 Role --> Passenger : [Role: Passenger]
 Role --> Admin : [Role: Admin]
}

state \"System Error\" as Error {
 state \"Connection Lost\" as ConnLost
 state \"GPS Signal Failure\" as GPSLost
}

' Global Transitions
Launched --> Guest : Start App
Guest --> Auth : Login Success 
Auth --> Guest : Logout 
Auth --> Error : [Network/GPS Issue]
Error --> Auth : Retry Connection

@enduml",
 "format": "svg"
